  "additionalProperties": false,
  "$id": "https://formael.dev/schemas/actlint/report.schema.json",
  "title": "actlint report",
  "description": "actlint's --json report: a versioned, machine-readable account of one server's action-risk honesty. The canonical output is `findings`; `grade` and `summary` are deterministic reductions of it. This schema is a public API — its shape changes only on a semver decision."
